title: Mastodon Discography 2000-2014 (v2.0)
description:
Another version of the same torrent. Just in case, as my uploads tend to have a pretty sketchy hit-to-miss ratio. If I cared, I probably would've figured out why and done something about it. Oh well.


Good luck finding a better Mastodon torrent anywhere on the interwebz. That's all I'll say. Just look at this shit:

Can you beat that? Huh? Can you? I'd like to see you try, punk.

I'd sure like to see you try.
